      "side": 1,
      "message": "I see the need for the new object mapper in order to handle the links correctly. But I\u0027m wondering why not use the getAssociatedSubTreePaths()/getAssociatedSubTreePathsById() when finding the owned fans?\n\nSeems like the original getFanPaths() function could still be used but just add the check of the BMCWEB_REDFISH_FAN_LINKS to determine which association should be used to retrieve the object paths.",
